'''Arvo Norstag''' was the original [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] [[King of the Phosphura Belt Pirates|king]] of the [[Phosphura Belt Pirates]]. He wrote many of the laws and codexes that the Belt Pirates were known for, such as the [[Buccaneer Code]] and the [[Rules of the Blade]].<ref name="ZA">{{JournalCite|5|Zirtran's Anchor (article)}}</ref>

